==How do I purchase road's vehicles?==

# To build a [[en/Manual/Road vehicles|road vehicle]], [[en/Manual/Building road depots|place a depot]] and then click it.
# You will be presented with the depot window. Select "Build new vehicles" and a new window will pop up with a list of vehicles.<br/>[[File:en/Manual/Tutorial bus 5.png|frame|none|Inside the depot...]]
# Select one and click "Buy Vehicle" at the bottom of this window.
# The vehicle will appear in the depot window and the vehicle's control window will open.
# Give it [[en/Manual/Orders]] or [[en/Manual/Refit]] it as necessary, then click on the red "Stopped" button to get it rolling!<br/>[[File:en/Manual/Stopped bus.png|frame|none|Inside the depot...]]

